headline: Alibaba gains, Amazon, Campbell's risk: Trending Tickers
summary: Market Domination host Josh Lipton and Yahoo Finance senior reporter Brooke DiPalma track several of the day's top trending stock tickers, including Alibaba's (BABA) stock gains after announcing a partnership with Nvidia (NVDA) and raising its AI spending plans above $50 billion, Wells Fargo's upgrade on Amazon shares (AMZN), and the analyst team out of BNP Paribas seeing market risk in the Campbell's Company (CPB). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
